OL,3,CThames Water to start fundraising
OL,4,Ctalks in coming weeks amid cash crisis
OL,6,FThames Water has said it will kick off
OL,7,Fthe process of raising more money from
OL,8,Finvestors over the next few weeks.
OL,10,FThe struggling water giant said that
OL,11,Fwhile it has been in talks with
OL,12,Fpotential funders since July, it will
OL,13,Flaunch its formal "equity solicitation
OL,14,Fprocess" in the coming weeks.
OL,16,FThat process is expected to drag on
OL,17,Fbeyond December, when regulator Ofwat
OL,18,Fpublishes its final verdict on water
OL,19,Ffirms' proposed plans for raising
OL,20,Fconsumer bills from 2025 until 2030.
