OL,3,CThames Water to start fundraising
OL,4,Ctalks in coming weeks amid cash crisis
OL,6,FThames Water, which serves about 16
OL,7,Fmillion people, is in the grip of a
OL,8,Ffunding crisis, and has only enough
OL,9,Fcash to continue operating until May
OL,10,F2025.
OL,12,FIt also has more than #15 billion of
OL,13,Fdebt, and Ofwat has said it intends to
OL,14,Fappoint an independent monitor to
OL,15,Fsupervise the company as it attempts a
OL,16,Fturnaround.
