OL,3,CThames Water to start fundraising
OL,4,Ctalks in coming weeks amid cash crisis
OL,6,FIf Thames Water does not raise fresh
OL,7,Fcash, it faces a potential
OL,8,Fnationalisation next year, something
OL,9,Fthe Labour Government has said it is
OL,10,Fkeen to avoid.
OL,12,FThames Water is at the centre of a
OL,13,Fpublic row over steep proposed hikes
OL,14,Fto water bills, which have sparked
OL,15,Foutrage amid a growing crisis around
OL,16,Ffirms' polluting of waterways with
OL,17,Fsewage spills.
