OL,3,CThames Water to start fundraising
OL,4,Ctalks in coming weeks amid cash crisis
OL,6,FAs of August 31, the company had about
OL,7,F#1.57 billion in cash. However, #380
OL,8,Fmillion of that is currently locked up
OL,9,Fas "reserves" under its current
OL,10,Ffunding agreements.
OL,12,FIt said on Friday that it has asked
OL,13,Fits creditors to allow it to access
OL,14,Fthat #380 million, otherwise it will
OL,15,F"enter standstill" by the end of
OL,16,FDecember.
OL,18,FIn that case, it would still have two
OL,19,Ffurther sources of potential funding
OL,20,Fto see it through to May.
