OL,3,CThames Water to start fundraising
OL,4,Ctalks in coming weeks amid cash crisis
OL,6,FOne is in the form of #420 million of
OL,7,FClass A and Class B "undrawn committed
OL,8,Ffacilities", which are a type of
OL,9,Fcredit agreement.
OL,11,FAnother is a #550 million pot of
OL,12,F"undrawn reserve liquidity
OL,13,Ffacilities", it said.
OL,15,FAll the funding combined will see it
OL,16,Fthrough to the end of May 2025. The
OL,17,Ffresh fundraising which it plans to
OL,18,Fstart in the coming weeks is designed
OL,19,Fto extend beyond that point.
